snippet.title: Launch Trailer - Might & Magic Heroes III HD Edition
snippet.description:
Available now on http://shop.ubi.com/Heroes3HD

The legendary Might & Magic® Heroes® III is back in HD. Enjoy the critically acclaimed gameplay with a new online multiplayer mode and forge the destinies of mighty and magical heroes now!

More info on http://mmh3-hd.com
